data.text:
Jahmal Jones - Points

Jahmal Jones scores a career high 32 points (2015)

On November 18, 2015, Jahmal Jones set his career high in points in a Czech Republic - Mattoni NBL game. That day he scored 32 points in Svitavy's home loss against Hradec, 75-80. He also had 7 rebounds, 7 assists. He shot 5/11 from two, 5/9 from three, shooting at 50.0% from the field. He also shot 7/7 from the free-throw line.

Jahmal Jones - Rebounds

Jahmal Jones grabs a career high 13 rebounds (2016)

On February 07, 2016, Jahmal Jones set his career high in rebounds in a Czech Republic - Mattoni NBL game. That day he grabbed 13 rebounds in Svitavy's home win against Kolin, 74-63. He also had 12 points, 6 assists, 2 steals.

Jahmal Jones - Assists

Jahmal Jones gives a career high 11 assists (2015)

On October 10, 2015, Jahmal Jones tied his career high in assists in a Czech Republic - Mattoni NBL game. That day he dished 11 assists in Svitavy's road win against Hradec, 76-80. He also had 17 points, 6 rebounds, 4 steals.

Jahmal Jones - Steals

Jahmal Jones has a career high 6 steals (2016)

On April 02, 2016, Jahmal Jones set his career high in steals in a Czech Republic - Mattoni NBL game. That day he reached 6 steals in Svitavy's home win against Decin, 84-73. He also had 13 points, 8 rebounds and 6 assists.

Jahmal Jones - Blocks

Jahmal Jones blocks a career high 2 shots (2016)

On March 02, 2016, Jahmal Jones set his career high in blocks in a Czech Republic - Mattoni NBL game. That day he went for 2 blocks in Svitavy's home win against Opava, 83-75. He also had 6 points, 2 rebounds and 4 assists.

Jahmal Jones - Efficiency

Jahmal Jones records a career high 43 efficiency rating (2020)

On February 16, 2020, Jahmal Jones set his career high in efficiency in a Denmark - Ligaen game. That day he accomplished 43 efficiency in Team FOG Naestved's road win against Horsens IC, 94-103. He also had 30 points, 6 rebounds and 9 assists.
